        <span class="inline-block bg-ceylon-gold-400 text-ceylon-green-900 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">Photography</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif font-black text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl leading-tight">Sri Lanka Photography Guide: Best Spots, Light & Tips</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-white/70 text-sm mt-4">
          <span>April 2026</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>8 min read</span>
        </div>
